---
Title: Contemplation's Brevity, and Why Knowledge and Imagination
  Can't Acquire It
Source:
  - Title: The Cloud of Unknowing
    Chapter: 4
    Page: 13
    Translator: Carmen Acevedo Butcher
    ISBN: 978-1-59030-622-1
    LOCN: BV5082.3.C58 2009
---
Lift up your heart to God with a gentle stirring of Love.
Focus on Him alone.
Want Him, and not anything He's made.
Think on nothing but Him.
Don't let anything else run through your mind and will.
